name: Invesco S&P 500 Equal Weight Index ETF
longDescription: Invesco S&P 500 Equal Weight Index ETF (the ETF) seeks to replicate, before fees and expenses, the performance of its underlying index, the S&P 500 Equal Weight Index, on an unhedged basis, in the case of any unhedged units, or on a hedged basis, in the case of any hedged units.
